task.summary: added new SqlLocator simplified storage system
Deleted FilePathSqlLocator Dao classes no longer needs to be implemented by the specific db adaper Restructured the file locations
Refactored/restructured alot so now we can change emailAddress if needed
extracted the sql locating logic into a static method

renamed somethingData objects to something and something objects to somethingEntity
e.g. userData is now user and user is now userEntity
relocated senders, users and their related classes into their own package
added a hardClean script which will drop all the tables. useful when changing table schema during dev
moved test classes around using a new naming scheme for tests added common test cases for accessors.txt -> guideline on how to write tests for other accessors
